  "style": "APA",
  "texts": [
    "Research into pruning (Cussens 2012; Suzuki 2017; de Campos et al. 2018; Correia et al. 2020) which can reduce the size of this cache whilst maintaining the guarantee of optimality has been important to the development of exact search.",
    "Most of the later pruning approaches are specific to a particular score (e.g.",
    "BIC or BDeu) and can have a dramatic effect on the cache size and search space considered.",
    "De Campos and Ji (2010) reported cache size being reduced by between approximately 10 2 and 10 7 times depending upon the network and specific score considered.",
    "In the most dramatic cases, this resulted in a reduction of the search space by hundreds of orders of magnitude."
  ],
  "correct_citations": [
    "Research into pruning (Cussens 2012; Suzuki 2017; de Campos et al. 2018; Correia et al. 2020) which can reduce the size of this cache whilst maintaining the guarantee of optimality has been important to the development of exact search."
  ]
}